00:26:42.360 --> 00:26:43.416
- Okay? - Yes.

00:26:44.280 --> 00:26:46.760
Wow, if I didn’t know he’s an athlete,

00:26:46.800 --> 00:26:48.096
I’d swear he’s a doctor.

