Say it, Mr. Inthu.

00:35:30.590 --> 00:35:31.590
It’s good.

00:35:33.020 --> 00:35:33.968
What was that?

00:35:34.008 --> 00:35:35.392
It’s good, alright?

00:35:36.380 --> 00:35:37.736
Pour the water of dedication.

00:35:59.580 --> 00:36:01.976
Is it difficult living here?

00:36:03.070 --> 00:36:04.504
Not at all, Venerable Grandfather.

00:36:06.264 --> 00:36:08.736
In can be a little stubborn.

00:36:08.784 --> 00:36:10.472
Don’t take it personally.

00:36:11.160 --> 00:36:12.824
He’s just been on his own for a long time.

00:36:12.848 --> 00:36:13.896
Venerable Grandfather,

00:36:15.220 --> 00:36:18.352
In wasn’t like this before?

00:36:18.376 --> 00:36:21.120
Back then, he was full of spirit.

00:36:21.460 --> 00:36:24.008
But after he lost his parents,

00:36:24.040 --> 00:36:27.552
he grew quiet and withdrawn.

00:36:28.040 --> 00:36:30.040
His house here was left abandoned.

00:36:30.490 --> 00:36:34.456
Village Chief Ju and the villagers have been looking after it for him.

00:36:34.784 --> 00:36:36.780
Otherwise, it’d be a wreck.

00:36:37.830 --> 00:36:40.472
Like the flower garden up there.

00:36:41.420 --> 00:36:42.960
There’s a flower garden?

00:36:43.630 --> 00:36:46.768
His father planted it for his wife

00:36:46.800 --> 00:36:49.288
and son when In was born.

00:36:49.620 --> 00:36:53.568
And what about his ability to see people’s futures?

00:36:54.210 --> 00:36:56.080
That’s something else entirely.

00:36:56.512 --> 00:36:58.510
In doesn’t want to see them,

00:36:59.140 --> 00:37:01.520
but fate left him no choice.

00:37:01.576 --> 00:37:05.120
That’s why he keeps to himself and avoids others.

00:37:05.740 --> 00:37:08.848
Because when he sees, he wants to help.

00:37:08.888 --> 00:37:11.416
