00:37:17.496 --> 00:37:19.576
Don’t overthink it.

00:37:19.608 --> 00:37:23.528
He helps you because he truly wants to.

00:37:24.230 --> 00:37:28.376
Even though he knows he must take the fall instead?

00:37:31.520 --> 00:37:35.392
Have you ever heard that nothing in this world is a coincidence?

00:37:36.020 --> 00:37:41.984
You two crossing paths, it was meant to be.

00:37:42.656 --> 00:37:44.660
This misfortune is serious.

00:37:46.230 --> 00:37:49.488
You must stay calm, be patient,

00:37:49.512 --> 00:37:51.200
and look after each other.

00:37:52.780 --> 00:37:53.944
Yes, sir.

