You’ll see.

00:40:44.060 --> 00:40:45.032
Come on!

00:40:45.056 --> 00:40:46.088
Okay, okay.

00:40:46.460 --> 00:40:47.460
Hurry up.

00:40:52.320 --> 00:40:56.368
Come on, have a seat.

00:40:56.400 --> 00:40:57.640
Thank you.

00:40:58.420 --> 00:40:59.056
Thank you.

00:40:59.104 --> 00:41:00.232
Wow, Auntie Pian.

00:41:03.460 --> 00:41:04.672
Thank you.

00:41:05.030 --> 00:41:11.544
Thap and Khaohom teamed up to surprise In.

00:41:12.940 --> 00:41:13.940
Really?

00:41:18.510 --> 00:41:21.344
Thap’s amazing.

00:41:21.360 --> 00:41:22.672
He hasn’t even been here that long,

00:41:22.696 --> 00:41:24.384
but he’s already helped so many villagers.

